screen_desc: The screenshot displays a messaging app interface titled "New Message." It includes options to create a "New Group," "New Secret Chat," and "New Channel." Below these options, there is a list of contacts sorted by their last seen time, showing names and timestamps indicating when they were last active. The contacts include various names, some with profile pictures, and the last seen times range from a few minutes ago to the previous day.
